OL,3,CGB News bosses summoned by Ofcom after
OL,4,CLaurence Fox broke broadcasting rules
OL,6,FOfcom also said it has 'significant
OL,7,Fconcerns' about GB News' live output,
OL,8,FITV News' Neil Connery reports
OL,10,FMedia watchdog Ofcom has ruled
OL,11,FLaurence Fox's "misogynistic" comments
OL,12,Fabout journalist Ava Evans on Dan
OL,13,FWootton's GB News show broke
OL,14,Fbroadcasting rules which protect
OL,15,F"viewers from offensive content".
OL,17,FThe watchdog has said the offence has
OL,18,Fraised "significant concerns about GB
OL,19,FNews' editorial control of its live
OL,20,Foutput."
