OL,6,FIt has summoned channel bosses to its
OL,7,Foffices to provide further information
OL,8,Fabout GB News' compliance practices
OL,9,Ffor Ofcom's consideration.
OL,11,FThe episode in which Fox made on-air
OL,12,Fremarks about journalist Ava Evans was
OL,13,Fthe most complained-about TV event of
OL,14,Fthe year, revealed.
