OL,3,CGB News bosses summoned by Ofcom after
OL,4,CLaurence Fox broke broadcasting rules
OL,6,FThe episode, which was broadcast on GB
OL,7,FNews on September 26, received 8,867
OL,8,Fcomplaints with viewers objecting to
OL,9,Fthe "misogynistic comments" made by
OL,10,Factor-turned-politician Fox about
OL,11,Fabout political correspondent Ms
OL,12,FEvans, including asking "who would
OL,13,Fwant to s*** that?"
OL,15,F"We found that Mr Fox's comments
OL,16,Fconstituted a highly personal attack
OL,17,Fon Ms Evans and were potentially
OL,18,Fhighly offensive to viewers," Ofcom
OL,19,Fsaid.
