OL,4,CLaurence Fox broke broadcasting rules
OL,6,FThey added Wootton's reaction did not
OL,7,Fmitigate the potential for offence but
OL,8,Frather "exacerbated it" by
OL,9,F"contributing to the narrative in
OL,10,Fwhich a woman's value was judged by
OL,11,Fher physical appearance".
OL,13,FFox responded to the ruling on Monday
OL,14,Fin a series of posts on X, formerly
OL,15,FTwitter, saying that he is not "overly
OL,16,Fbothered about this anymore."
