OL,3,CGB News bosses summoned by Ofcom after
OL,4,CLaurence Fox broke broadcasting rules
OL,6,F"I could have expressed myself better,
OL,7,Fthat's life and I've said my bit. I
OL,8,Fstill think it's one of the biggest
OL,9,Fpieces of confected outrage I've ever
OL,10,Fwitnessed".
OL,12,FHe added that everything said on air
OL,13,Fwas "discussed and agreed with the
OL,14,Fproduction team beforehand" and that
OL,15,Fthey were "laughing and joking about
OL,16,Fit".
OL,18,F"GB News also has a delay, so they
OL,19,Fcould have just cut the feed, but they
OL,20,Fdidn't."
