OL,3,CGB News bosses summoned by Ofcom after
OL,4,CLaurence Fox broke broadcasting rules
OL,6,FGB News has been contacted for comment.
OL,8,FFox and presenter Wootton, who later
OL,9,Fboth apologised, were suspended by the
OL,10,Fchannel after the broadcast and Fox
OL,11,Fhas since been sacked by the channel.
OL,13,FThe incident narrowly beat Bridgerton
OL,14,Fstar Adjoah Andoh's comments made
OL,15,Fduring ITV's coverage of the King's
OL,16,Fcoronation to the top spot of the
OL,17,Fmedia watchdog's annual list.
